## Requirements
🖥️ System Requirements
Windows 10 / 11 (recommended)
Python 3.10+
VS Code (optional but recommended)
📦 Python Libraries

Install the following dependencies:

pip install flask pandas matplotlib

(Optional for future upgrades)

pip install chart.js

 ## Procedure
1️⃣ Clone / Download Project
git clone <your-repo-link>
cd mood_app
OR simply download ZIP and extract.

2️⃣ Install Dependencies
Run:
pip install flask pandas matplotlib
 
3️⃣ Run the Application
python app.py

4️⃣ Open in Browser
Go to:
http://127.0.0.1:5001

 5️⃣ How to Use
Select your mood 😊😐😔😴😡
Write optional thoughts 📝
Click Save

## View:
💬 Personalized AI-style quotes
🔥 Mood streak
📊 Mood trend graph
6️⃣ Auto Start (Optional)

## To run on startup:

Create .bat file:
python C:\path\to\app.py
start http://127.0.0.1:5000
Move it to:
shell:startup
